  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><br><strong>Bounce Quest </strong>is a brutally challenging platformer where you take control of a little bouncy cube on a mission to climb a dangerous mountain and uncover the secret hidden at its peak. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/6213c5740e6814b5bff02e04f5780096.poster.avif?t=1751296510\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/6213c5740e6814b5bff02e04f5780096.webm?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/6213c5740e6814b5bff02e04f5780096.mp4?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful during your journey, one wrong jump and you may be sent bouncing all the way to the bottom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/d6592d3fba2da2699741bc681465a7f2.poster.avif?t=1751296510\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/d6592d3fba2da2699741bc681465a7f2.webm?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/d6592d3fba2da2699741bc681465a7f2.mp4?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong><br><br><strong>In this game you can:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fall</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repeat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and <strong>maybe</strong> get a step higher each time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2610cfa64ab0d44292549e27202f1e45.poster.avif?t=1751296510\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2610cfa64ab0d44292549e27202f1e45.webm?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2610cfa64ab0d44292549e27202f1e45.mp4?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 6 unique areas each packed with tricky gimmicks and challenges to make your climb harder and unlock 12 collectible cube skins scattered around the map to customize your bounce as you go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2a6a0b033cf38e4c3fe7f6e83a093d9b.poster.avif?t=1751296510\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2a6a0b033cf38e4c3fe7f6e83a093d9b.webm?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2a6a0b033cf38e4c3fe7f6e83a093d9b.mp4?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Soundtrack made entirely by <strong>AlphaLynx</strong>, check out his YouTube channel! <br> <br> <br> <br><i>\"The higher you go, the harder you will fall\"</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><br><strong>Bounce Quest </strong>is a brutally challenging platformer where you take control of a little bouncy cube on a mission to climb a dangerous mountain and uncover the secret hidden at its peak. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/6213c5740e6814b5bff02e04f5780096.poster.avif?t=1751296510\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/6213c5740e6814b5bff02e04f5780096.webm?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/6213c5740e6814b5bff02e04f5780096.mp4?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful during your journey, one wrong jump and you may be sent bouncing all the way to the bottom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/d6592d3fba2da2699741bc681465a7f2.poster.avif?t=1751296510\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/d6592d3fba2da2699741bc681465a7f2.webm?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/d6592d3fba2da2699741bc681465a7f2.mp4?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong><br><br><strong>In this game you can:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fall</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repeat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and <strong>maybe</strong> get a step higher each time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2610cfa64ab0d44292549e27202f1e45.poster.avif?t=1751296510\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2610cfa64ab0d44292549e27202f1e45.webm?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2610cfa64ab0d44292549e27202f1e45.mp4?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 6 unique areas each packed with tricky gimmicks and challenges to make your climb harder and unlock 12 collectible cube skins scattered around the map to customize your bounce as you go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2a6a0b033cf38e4c3fe7f6e83a093d9b.poster.avif?t=1751296510\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2a6a0b033cf38e4c3fe7f6e83a093d9b.webm?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302270/extras/2a6a0b033cf38e4c3fe7f6e83a093d9b.mp4?t=1751296510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Soundtrack made entirely by <strong>AlphaLynx</strong>, check out his YouTube channel! <br> <br> <br> <br><i>\"The higher you go, the harder you will fall\"</i></p>",
